<L>"Who&s;e well-fought fields bear record of his name.</L>
<L>"To guard his country, and to check his foes,</L>
<L>"By <HI>Randolph</HI>'s hands this glorious fabric ro&s;e:</L>
<L>"Tho' now in ruin'd heaps thy bulwarks lie,</L>
<L>"Revolving time &s;hall rai&s;e tho&s;e bulwarks high,</L>
