<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">es, <HI>Filioli cavete vobis ab idolis;</HI> and above their heads are <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> lines:
